## 3. Capitalization Rules

- **Product name**: Always capitalize as branded (e.g., "OrrisTech")
- **Feature names**: Lowercase unless it is a branded product feature
- **Headings**: Sentence case ("Getting started with the API") not title case
- **Buttons**: Sentence case ("Create account") not all caps
- **UI labels**: Sentence case throughout
- **Acronyms**: All caps, no periods (API, URL, SEO, HTML)

