## 5. Common Phrases

### CTAs

- "Get started" (primary)
- "Learn more" (secondary)
- "View docs" (for documentation links)
- "Try it free" (for trial signups)

### Confirmation / Success

- "Done." or "Saved." (not "Successfully saved!")
- "Your changes have been saved." (for important actions)

### Errors

- Lead with what happened, then what to do: "Could not save changes. Check your connection and try again."
- Never blame the user: "Something went wrong" not "You entered an invalid value"

